{"tid":1848751,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[行動129]黎明行動 召喚嘔吐師-和理勇","createTime":"2020-01-28T15:44:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-29T12:34:55.000Z","uid":256620,"like":70,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":49,"replies":[{"pid":"ce0248e045316459d2f599a1ecd4408ef086c94d","tid":1848751,"uid":256620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T15:44:11.000Z","msg":"香城ONLINE一個被遺忘已久的職業 嘔吐師<br />\n原PO <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1709692/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1709692/page/1</a><br />\n推唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n聽朝7AM見<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n嘔吐師/病人<br />\n攻擊力:0<br />\n防禦力:0<br />\n職業簡介:一個身體唔舒服，但都要繼續返工嘅港豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n特殊能力:嘔吐<br />\n<br />\n新手道具<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HOj6qG1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHOj6qG1.jpg&h=5506cf3c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n早餐<br />\n簡介:日日返工都驚遲到，所以進化出喺車箱都方便食到嘅早餐<br />\n<br />\n技能<br />\n嘔吐<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VFX7UAm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVFX7UAm.png&h=0c9eefd4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/68RgNVn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F68RgNVn.png&h=cbb877c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n使用次數:2 (因為一包餅得兩塊)<br />\n使用道具早餐後，因為車廂中不能進食而無法吞嚥，適當時候反胃即可。<br />\n技能效果:範圍內生人勿近，進一步壓縮車廂空間，包保咩陣營嘅人都想同你保持距離，輕鬆霸走1/3個車廂<br />\n<br />\n但要留意濺射範圍，因為和理非係零攻擊力，所以盡量唔好射中人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n要改進嘅係塊餅嚼得太爛，似朱奶多過嘔吐物，睇吓升高啲lv 之後會唔會再似啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n之後可以行出車廂，或者進一步叫職員協助清理，由得下個站佢地自己搞<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/X8ZigQB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FX8ZigQB.jpg&h=dce9ca4d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f8b50bc9c2d38218f485e1f977d6c98a6a17558e","tid":1848751,"uid":130740,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T15:45:28.000Z","msg":"推啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />岀黎既手足唔係condom<br />\n抗疫黎明唔夠多人就等於預約被捕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">手足幫手推行動post啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n【抗疫黎明】屌你老母成個熱門都冇行動post<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1848717\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1848717</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n除咗三罷，抗疫黎明都好緊要㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n聽朝0700各區開花 抗疫黎明 配合三罷<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eufELEL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeufELEL.jpg&h=f4da908a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nCyu7S6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnCyu7S6.jpg&h=a67b68c8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fx2Porr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ffx2Porr.jpg&h=51368852&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"dca746b06e9d7bed9791411ba3f472b37c65319f","tid":1848751,"uid":5483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T15:51:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8b804b727df8e95333d626a7023845eb4b11b126","tid":1848751,"uid":92038,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T15:53:27.000Z","msg":"推爆佢<br />\n推爆佢<br />\n推爆佢"},{"pid":"d559823236b73e8f9228ebd2e5cc6ef54589ac97","tid":1848751,"uid":10630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T15:53:54.000Z","msg":"好正 要推"},{"pid":"728dc002c974bd0eb06050674f8a295d56a1cfd5","tid":1848751,"uid":98993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T15:54:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9f8f3e21ad3beb984e6ec956f675ad18b4a433df","tid":1848751,"uid":98993,"like":0,"dis